{"type":"message","id":"7367c62b","parentId":"cb9db530","timestamp":"2026-05-21T19:03:26.469Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"74e04d5a-5635-4fa4-8f52-4066c602f3bd","toolName":"cron","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"jobs\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"dae7406b-ec78-4752-ba93-91bc62541f7d\",\n      \"agentId\": \"main\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:main:telegram:direct:7507878944\",\n      \"name\": \"Daily Station Check\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1778891325409,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"cron\",\n        \"expr\": \"0 23 * * *\",\n        \"tz\": \"Europe/London\"\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"Run the daily station check and send a Telegram sitrep. Do NOT use any AI model calls — just use shell commands and file operations.\\n\\n1. **System Health**: Run `sysctl vm.loadavg`, `df -h / | tail -1`, `vm_stat | head -5`, `uptime`. Log results to `memory/health-log.md` with timestamp.\\n\\n2. **Git Auto-Commit**: Check `cd ~/.openclaw/workspace/mission-control-dashboard && git status --porcelain`. If there are changes, run `git add -A && git commit -m \\\"auto: daily commit\\\" && git push`. Log result.\\n\\n3. **Task Cleanup**: Read `data/tasks.json`. Archive any completed tasks older than 30 days to `data/tasks-archive.json`. Log count.\\n\\n4. **Backup Check**: Check if `/Volumes/OpenClaw-WD` or `/Volumes/Public` is mounted. Check if today's backup file exists. Log result.\\n\\n5. **Daily Summary**: Append a brief summary to `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md` with: date, system health snapshot, git commit status, tasks archived, backup status.\\n\\n6. **Telegram Sitrep**: Use `curl` to send a one-line daily sitrep to Telegram chat 7507878944 via the OpenClaw gateway message API. The sitrep should include: tasks active count, tasks awaiting review count, disk %, and overall status (nominal/fail). Format example:\\n   `📡 DAILY SITREP — 2026-05-16 | 3 active · 1 awaiting review · 85% disk · ✅ ALL SYSTEMS NOMINAL`\\n   \\n   If disk > 90% or any critical issues found, use `⚠️` instead and note the issue.\\n   \\n   Use the OpenClaw gateway to send: `openclaw message send --channel telegram --to 7507878944 \\\"<sitrep text>\\\"` or use the gateway HTTP API at localhost:18789.\\n\\nKeep it fast. Use exec for all operations. Do not call any models.\",\n        \"timeoutSeconds\": 120\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"announce\",\n        \"channel\": \"last\",\n        \"to\": \"7507878944\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1779400800000,\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1779314400008,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 90984,\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"delivered\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 0,\n        \"consecutiveSkipped\": 0,\n        \"lastFailureNotificationDeliveryStatus\": \"not-requested\",\n        \"lastDelivered\": true\n      },\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1779314490992\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"6f823429-453b-4db5-a5c9-51472f1693b3\",\n      \"agentId\": \"main\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:main:main\",\n      \"name\": \"Sessions Cleanup\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1779373498843,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"cron\",\n        \"expr\": \"0 2 * * *\",\n        \"tz\": \"UTC\"\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"main\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"systemEvent\",\n        \"text\": \"openclaw sessions cleanup\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1779415200000\n      },\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1779373802826\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"c52ff1a0-0936-48f9-8247-3711020824ca\",\n      \"agentId\": \"main\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:main:main\",\n      \"name\": \"Session Auto‑Expiry\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1779373821493,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"cron\",\n        \"expr\": \"0 4 * * *\",\n        \"tz\": \"UTC\"\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"main\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"systemEvent\",\n        \"text\": \"/Users/spacemonkey/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/session-expiry.sh\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1779422400000\n      },\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1779373821493\n    }\n  ],\n  \"total\": 3,\n  \"offset\": 0,\n  \"limit\": 3,\n  \"hasMore\": false,\n  \"nextOffset\": null,\n  \"deliveryPreviews\": {\n    \"dae7406b-ec78-4752-ba93-91bc62541f7d\": {\n      \"label\": \"announce -> telegram:7507878944\",\n      \"detail\": \"resolved from last, session agent:main:telegram:direct:7507878944\"\n    },\n    \"6f823429-453b-4db5-a5c9-51472f1693b3\": {\n      \"label\": \"not requested\",\n      \"detail\": \"not requested\"\n    },\n    \"c52ff1a0-0936-48f9-8247-3711020824ca\": {\n      \"label\": \"not requested\",\n      \"detail\": \"not requested\"\n    }\n  }\n}"}],"details":{"jobs":[{"id":"dae7406b-ec78-4752-ba93-91bc62541f7d","agentId":"main","sessionKey":"agent:main:telegram:direct:7507878944","name":"Daily Station Check","enabled":true,"createdAtMs":1778891325409,"schedule":{"kind":"cron","expr":"0 23 * * *","tz":"Europe/London"},"sessionTarget":"isolated","wakeMode":"now","payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"Run the daily station check and send a Telegram sitrep. Do NOT use any AI model calls — just use shell commands and file operations.\n\n1. **System Health**: Run `sysctl vm.loadavg`, `df -h / | tail -1`, `vm_stat | head -5`, `uptime`. Log results to `memory/health-log.md` with timestamp.\n\n2. **Git Auto-Commit**: Check `cd ~/.openclaw/workspace/mission-control-dashboard && git status --porcelain`. If there are changes, run `git add -A && git commit -m \"auto: daily commit\" && git push`. Log result.\n\n3. **Task Cleanup**: Read `data/tasks.json`. Archive any completed tasks older than 30 days to `data/tasks-archive.json`. Log count.\n\n4. **Backup Check**: Check if `/Volumes/OpenClaw-WD` or `/Volumes/Public` is mounted. Check if today's backup file exists. Log result.\n\n5. **Daily Summary**: Append a brief summary to `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md` with: date, system health snapshot, git commit status, tasks archived, backup status.\n\n6. **Telegram Sitrep**: Use `curl` to send a one-line daily sitrep to Telegram chat 7507878944 via the OpenClaw gateway message API. The sitrep should include: tasks active count, tasks awaiting review count, disk %, and overall status (nominal/fail). Format example:\n   `📡 DAILY SITREP — 2026-05-16 | 3 active · 1 awaiting review · 85% disk · ✅ ALL SYSTEMS NOMINAL`\n   \n   If disk > 90% or any critical issues found, use `⚠️` instead and note the issue.\n   \n   Use the OpenClaw gateway to send: `openclaw message send --channel telegram --to 7507878944 \"<sitrep text>\"` or use the gateway HTTP API at localhost:18789.\n\nKeep it fast. Use exec for all operations. Do not call any models.","timeoutSeconds":120},"delivery":{"mode":"announce","channel":"last","to":"7507878944"},"state":{"nextRunAtMs":1779400800000,"lastRunAtMs":1779314400008,"lastRunStatus":"ok","lastStatus":"ok","lastDurationMs":90984,"lastDeliveryStatus":"delivered","consecutiveErrors":0,"consecutiveSkipped":0,"lastFailureNotificationDeliveryStatus":"not-requested","lastDelivered":true},"updatedAtMs":1779314490992},{"id":"6f823429-453b-4db5-a5c9-51472f1693b3","agentId":"main","sessionKey":"agent:main:main","name":"Sessions Cleanup","enabled":true,"createdAtMs":1779373498843,"schedule":{"kind":"cron","expr":"0 2 * * *","tz":"UTC"},"sessionTarget":"main","wakeMode":"now","payload":{"kind":"systemEvent","text":"openclaw sessions cleanup"},"state":{"nextRunAtMs":1779415200000},"updatedAtMs":1779373802826},{"id":"c52ff1a0-0936-48f9-8247-3711020824ca","agentId":"main","sessionKey":"agent:main:main","name":"Session Auto‑Expiry","enabled":true,"createdAtMs":1779373821493,"schedule":{"kind":"cron","expr":"0 4 * * *","tz":"UTC"},"sessionTarget":"main","wakeMode":"now","payload":{"kind":"systemEvent","text":"/Users/spacemonkey/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/session-expiry.sh"},"state":{"nextRunAtMs":1779422400000},"updatedAtMs":1779373821493}],"total":3,"offset":0,"limit":3,"hasMore":false,"nextOffset":null,"deliveryPreviews":{"dae7406b-ec78-4752-ba93-91bc62541f7d":{"label":"announce -> telegram:7507878944","detail":"resolved from last, session agent:main:telegram:direct:7507878944"},"6f823429-453b-4db5-a5c9-51472f1693b3":{"label":"not requested","detail":"not requested"},"c52ff1a0-0936-48f9-8247-3711020824ca":{"label":"not requested","detail":"not requested"}}},"isError":false,"timestamp":1779390206465}}
{"type":"message","id":"6ef50bae","parentId":"7367c62b","timestamp":"2026-05-21T19:03:42.297Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The remaining 3 cron jobs are all reasonable — they run once daily and each does useful work:\n\n- **Daily Station Check** — daily Telegram sitrep (once/day, 90s runtime, delivers to you). This is fine.\n- **Sessions Cleanup** — daily session cleanup at 2am. But our LaunchAgent already does this every 30 min. Redundant.\n- **Session Auto-Expiry** — daily session expiry at 4am. Also redundant now.\n\nLet me disable the two redundant ones:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"bbc554c1-e166-4837-ab93-28d4443c2075","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"update","jobId":"6f823429-453b-4db5-a5c9-51472f1693b3","patch":{"enabled":false}},"partialArgs":"{\"action\": \"update\", \"jobId\": \"6f823429-453b-4db5-a5c9-51472f1693b3\", \"patch\": {\"enabled\": false}}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"40f4a17e-bc43-41de-b1d6-29a786f8f16f","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"update","jobId":"c52ff1a0-0936-48f9-8247-3711020824ca","patch":{"enabled":false}},"partialArgs":"{\"action\": \"update\", \"jobId\": \"c52ff1a0-0936-48f9-8247-3711020824ca\", \"patch\": {\"enabled\": false}}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/owl-alpha","usage":{"input":1627,"output":246,"cacheRead":51328,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":53201,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779390206470,"responseId":"gen-1779390206-C2x3qS2vWtpidq2BT1pM"}}
