{"type":"message","id":"e956b476","parentId":"481012c2","timestamp":"2026-05-21T19:12:57.162Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"f2ae7dcb-73f7-49f8-8d7d-9c85ed470617","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"INC-012 | TRIAGE       | 2026-05-16 | ['wrangler', 'mission-control', 'launchagent', 'outage', 'backfill-2026-05-16'] | Mission Control down — LaunchAgent pointing to deleted Wrangler binary\nINC-011 | TRIAGE       | 2026-05-16 | ['all-keys-exhausted', 'rate-limit', 'models', '429', 'backfill-2026-05-16'] | Rate limit exhaustion — all models returned 429 starting May 15 19:42\nINC-010 | TRIAGE       | 2026-05-16 | ['failures', 'git', 'cron', 'activity-summary', 'backfill-2026-05-16'] | Cron job failures — Git Auto-Commit timeout and Activity Summary failing\nINC-009 | TRIAGE       | 2026-05-16 | ['wd-mycloud', 'backup', 'mount', 'storage', 'backfill-2026-05-16'] | WD MyCloud mount failing — /Volumes/Public-1 not found (persistent since May 16 06:18)\nINC-008 | TRIAGE       | 2026-05-16 | ['tasks', 'orphaned', 'in-progress', 'stale', 'backfill-2026-05-16'] | Tasks stuck In Progress — 3 tasks with no assignee or recent activity\nINC-007 | TRIAGE       | 2026-05-16 | ['ssr', 'animation', 'build', 'dashboard', 'backfill-2026-05-16'] | Build error — AnimatePresence SSR failure in Dashboard component\nINC-006 | TRIAGE       | 2026-05-16 | ['dev-server', 'launchagent', 'conflict', 'port', 'backfill-2026-05-16'] | Port conflict — Mission Control dev server jumping between 3000 and 3001\nINC-005 | TRIAGE       | 2026-05-16 | ['swap', 'disk', 'warning', 'storage', 'backfill-2026-05-16'] | Disk space warning — Data volume at 85% (175 Gi / 228 Gi)\nINC-004 | MITIGATING   | 2026-05-12 | ['memory', 'corruption', 'indexing', 'urgent'] | Memory index corruption after session restart\nINC-003 | RESOLVED     | 2026-05-11 | ['backup', 'wd-mycloud', 'permissions', 'smb'] | WD MyCloud SMB mount permissions broke backups\nINC-002 | TRIAGE       | 2026-05-12 | ['