{"type":"message","id":"1847b490","parentId":"d5ce30b6","timestamp":"2026-05-22T00:42:59.707Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"No backlog tasks. Let me also check if the in-progress work from the previous session (incident backfill + auto-detect fix + Quick Actions audit) needs completion. The auto-detect script had a bug I was about to fix:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"886c5636-975e-441f-91a8-0bfbde6973d3","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/spacemonkey/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/auto-detect-incidents.sh","offset":14,"limit":30},"partialArgs":"{\"path\": \"/Users/spacemonkey/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/auto-detect-incidents.sh\", \"offset\": 14, \"limit\": 30}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/owl-alpha","usage":{"input":296,"output":98,"cacheRead":52992,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":53386,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779410569189,"responseId":"gen-1779410569-YguZCxXuc92BQvMpLc0Q"}}
{"type":"message","id":"7db7fb69","parentId":"1847b490","timestamp":"2026-05-22T00:42:59.738Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"886c5636-975e-441f-91a8-0bfbde6973d3","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n# Helper: create incident via Python (since we need JSON manipulation)\ncreate_incident() {\n    local title=\"$1\" severity=\"$2\" owner=\"$3\" summary=\"$4\" tags=\"$5\" source=\"$6\"\n    python3 << PYEOF\nimport json, os\nfrom datetime import datetime\n\npath = \"$INCIDENTS_FILE\"\nincidents = json.load(open(path)) if os.path.exists(path) else []\n\n# Deduplicate\nfor i in incidents:\n    if i[\"status\"] != \"RESOLVED\" and i[\"title\"] == \"$title\" and \"$source\" in i.get(\"tags\", []):\n        print(\"duplicate\")\n        exit(0)\n\nnums = []\nfor i in incidents:\n    m = i[\"id\"].split(\"-\")\n    if len(m) == 2 and m[1].isdigit():\n        nums.append(int(m[1]))\nnext_id = f\"INC-{str(max(nums) + 1 if nums else 1).zfill(3)}\"\n\nnow = datetime.utcnow().strftime(\"%Y-%m-%dT%H:%M:%S.000Z\")\ninc = {\n    \"id\": next_id, \"title\": \"$title\", \"severity\": \"$severity\",\n    \"status\": \"TRIAGE\", \"owner\": \"$owner\", \"acknowledged\": False,\n    \"escalated\": False, \"opened\": now, \"lastActivity\": now,\n    \"summary\": \"$summary\",\n\n[184 more lines in file. Use offset=44 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1779410579738}}
{"type":"message","id":"8da6aad2","parentId":"7db7fb69","timestamp":"2026-05-22T00:43:19.109Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The `PYEOF` is unquoted, which means shell variables like `$INCIDENTS_FILE`, `$title`, `$severity` etc. inside the Python heredoc ARE being expanded by the shell. This is actually intentional for the `create_incident` function — the shell vars need to be interpolated into the Python code. But the issue from the test run was that `$WORKSPACE` was being expanded inside the Python code's `open()` call.\n\nLet me check what happened — the error said `.OPENCLAW_WORKSPACE` which means `$HOME` expanded but `OPENCLAW_WORKSPACE` was treated as a literal string. That's because in the Python code, the path uses `$WORKSPACE` which the shell expands — and `$WORKSPACE` is set to `$HOME/.openclaw/workspace`. Let me trace the actual issue:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"9921f84a-93f0-47af-afb9-a2f2c93ff0e2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Test the create_incident function manually\nINCIDENTS_FILE=\"/Users/spacemonkey/.openclaw/workspace/data/incidents.json\"\npython3 << 'PYEOF'\nimport json, os\nfrom datetime import datetime\n\npath = \"/Users/spacemonkey/.openclaw/workspace/data/incidents.json\"\nincidents = json.load(open(path)) if os.path.exists(path) else []\nprint(f\"Loaded {len(incidents)} incidents from {path}\")\nPYEOF"},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"# Test the create_incident function manually\\nINCIDENTS_FILE=\\\"/Users/spacemonkey/.openclaw/workspace/data/incidents.json\\\"\\npython3 << 'PYEOF'\\nimport json, os\\nfrom datetime import datetime\\n\\npath = \\\"/Users/spacemonkey/.openclaw/workspace/data/incidents.json\\\"\\nincidents = json.load(open(path)) if os.path.exists(path) else []\\nprint(f\\\"Loaded {len(incidents)} incidents from {path}\\\")\\nPYEOF\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/owl-alpha","usage":{"input":472,"output":290,"cacheRead":53248,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":54010,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779410579740,"responseId":"gen-1779410579-zavA3YWfOyb2eYExAy5d"}}
