{"type":"message","id":"3bdecc9d","parentId":"dcc9c6cf","timestamp":"2026-05-22T00:44:17.878Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Good — no duplicate incidents from the auto-detect run. The `create_incident` function failed before writing (the Python heredoc couldn't find the path), so nothing was created. The 18 incidents are all from the manual backfill. The auto-detect script needs the path fix. Let me trace the exact issue:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"6d9354f8-f21d-4d10-9657-7f3cd6db09f4","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# The issue: in the create_incident function, the Python heredoc uses unquoted PYEOF\n# This means $WORKSPACE inside the Python code gets shell-expanded\n# But $WORKSPACE is set at the top of the script to $HOME/.openclaw/workspace\n# The error showed .OPENCLAW_WORKSPACE which means $HOME expanded but OPENCLAW_WORKSPACE didn't\n# Wait — that's because the Python code has: path = \"$INCIDENTS_FILE\"\n# And $INCIDENTS_FILE = \"$WORKSPACE/data/incidents.json\"\n# So the shell expands $INCIDENTS_FILE to \"$HOME/.openclaw/workspace/data/incidents.json\"\n# Then Python sees: path = \"/Users/spacemonkey/.openclaw/workspace/data/incidents.json\"\n# That should work...\n\n# Let me actually test the function by running the script again\nbash /Users/spacemonkey/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/auto-detect-incidents.sh 2>&1\necho \"EXIT: $?\"","timeout":30},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"# The issue: in the create_incident function, the Python heredoc uses unquoted PYEOF\\n# This means $WORKSPACE inside the Python code gets shell-expanded\\n# But $WORKSPACE is set at the top of the script to $HOME/.openclaw/workspace\\n# The error showed .OPENCLAW_WORKSPACE which means $HOME expanded but OPENCLAW_WORKSPACE didn't\\n# Wait — that's because the Python code has: path = \\\"$INCIDENTS_FILE\\\"\\n# And $INCIDENTS_FILE = \\\"$WORKSPACE/data/incidents.json\\\"\\n# So the shell expands $INCIDENTS_FILE to \\\"$HOME/.openclaw/workspace/data/incidents.json\\\"\\n# Then Python sees: path = \\\"/Users/spacemonkey/.openclaw/workspace/data/incidents.json\\\"\\n# That should work...\\n\\n# Let me actually test the function by running the script again\\nbash /Users/spacemonkey/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/auto-detect-incidents.sh 2>&1\\necho \\\"EXIT: $?\\\"\", \"timeout\": 30}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/owl-alpha","usage":{"input":191,"output":309,"cacheRead":54528,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":55028,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779410639507,"responseId":"gen-1779410639-bJIw6SfeGmbYRz0mPdHE"}}
